headline: JM Smucker overhauls supply chain leadership
summary: The Milkbone maker named Rob Ferguson its new chief product supply officer after eliminating the COO role and announcing the retirement of several other supply chain executives.

headline: J. M. Smucker: I Don't Think You're Ready For This Jelly
summary: J. M. Smucker has achieved dividend aristocrat status with over 25 consecutive years of dividend increases and a current yield of 4.1%. Read why SJM is a Buy.

headline: JM Smucker axes COO role in leadership shake-up
summary: The restructure will see CFO Tucker Marshall expand his remit to executive vice president of frozen handheld, spreads and sweet baked snacks.
